---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="/now // rendoire" description="What I'm currently focused on.">
  <Navigation />
  
  <main id="main-content" class="article-page" style="min-height: 80vh; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 120px 2rem 4rem;">
    <article class="article-content reveal visible">
      <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to Home</a>
      
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 class="article-h1">/now</h1>
        <div class="article-date">Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', {month: 'long', year: 'numeric'})}</div>
      </header>
      
      <div class="formatted-content" style="opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); animation: none;">
        <p>This is a <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener">now page</a>. It documents what I am currently focused on.</p>
        
        <h2>Focus</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Building cade.golf:</strong> Shipping Phase 1 and monitoring early active user metrics. Expanding the social graph mechanics.</li>
          <li><strong>Live Service Resilience:</strong> Working heavily on infrastructure observability and scaling out high-throughput event queues.</li>
          <li><strong>Self-Hosting:</strong> Optimizing Proxmox topologies, tweaking local LLM response caching, and streamlining home-lab automation pipelines.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Reading</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><em>Designing Data-Intensive Applications</em> by Martin Kleppmann [reading]</li>
          <li><em>Zero to One</em> by Peter Thiel [finished 2024]</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Exploring</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Heavy lifting, trail running, and spending deliberate time disconnected from the digital world.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
